It's going to be either
1, 2 or 4 pi Dca.

00:38:20.460 --> 00:38:26.370
But there's some uptake
rate from each patch.

00:38:26.370 --> 00:38:28.726
But then that means just
that the uptake total

00:38:28.726 --> 00:38:31.465
for small numbers
