00:45:24.270 --> 00:45:25.710
about how much error.

00:45:25.710 --> 00:45:27.870
This is indeed just
the fractional error

00:45:27.870 --> 00:45:29.810
in our measurement
of the concentration,

00:45:29.810 --> 00:45:32.747
and irrespective
of whether the cell

00:45:32.747 --> 00:45:35.960
is able to estimate
the concentration

00:45:35.960 --> 00:45:38.010
units of a physical quantity.

00:45:38.010 --> 00:45:46.000
Because that sort of error
would scale together.

00:45:46.000 --> 00:45:48.517
I'm worried that I'm
not helping you, though.

00:45:48.517 --> 00:45:50.767
AUDIENCE: So you're kind of
saying because c and n are

00:45:50.767 --> 00:45:53.175
