00:47:06.500 --> 00:47:08.500
So then the variance no
longer equals the mean,

00:47:08.500 --> 00:47:09.750
so it's not a Poisson anymore.

00:47:09.750 --> 00:47:13.130
So you can't just multiply a
number times a Poisson to get--

00:47:13.130 --> 00:47:14.630
