If there's more
diffusion or higher

00:47:26.560 --> 00:47:29.790
concentration-- less error.

00:47:29.790 --> 00:47:32.820
And this is really in
some ways some estimate

00:47:32.820 --> 00:47:34.510
of the best the cell could do.

00:47:34.510 --> 00:47:38.490
And surprisingly, cells
can get close to this.

00:47:38.490 --> 00:47:42.790
Now, this is a measurement
of the concentration

